CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, May 17, 1938, pg. 26, reads: "Smoketown's lovelies and some of the celebrities in town over the week-end at the Loendi Club after the Junior Hostesses Fashion Show. Close scrutiny will reveal in above [below] picture Cab Calloway, Carl Nelson, Joe Louis, Thelma Spangler, Rosalind [Roslyn] Lindsay, Jackie Ormes and others swapping chatter. (Pgh. Photos by 'Teenie' Harris)."
TitMainTitle: Cab Calloway surrounded by nine women, including Roslyn Lindsay on left,  and Thelma Spangler third from left, posed around table in Loendi Club
